          "settings": {
            "question": "<strong>What is a \u201cProtocol\u201d?</strong>",
            "answer": "<p>A Protocol is a complete, evidence-based skincare system designed to work as a whole. Each step has a defined role, and products are sequenced for maximum efficacy.</p>"
